      "properties": {"Node name for S&R": "Note (生产配置说明)"},
      "widgets_values": ["=== 工业级 AI 视频变装管线 - 完整节点链条 ===\n\n【第一阶段：身份与底图】\n- LoadImage (参考脸) → ApplyPuLIDFlux (weight: 0.85)\n- EmptyLatentImage (1024x1024)\n- KSampler (Flux) CFG: 1.0, steps: 20\n\n【第二阶段：语义换衣】\n- VAEDecode: Flux潜空间 → 像素格式\n- IDM_VTON_LoadModel → IDM_VTON_Sampler\n- MaskEditor: 衣服遮罩微调\n\n【第三阶段：动态生成】\n- VAEEncode: 像素 → Wan2.1潜空间\n- WanVideoWrapper: BlockSwap 20 blocks\n- Wan2.1_I2V_Generator: Motion Bucket 127\n\n【第四阶段：封装输出】\n- TiledVAEDecode: 显存优化切片处理\n- ImageBatchToVideo: 帧排列\n- VHS_VideoCombine: FPS 24, 码率 20M\n\n=== 显存溢出预防 ===\n若OOM报警，调低 Wan2.1 帧数或启用 TiledVAE"]
    },
